    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "Re Doairtel, 3/9/60 and Detel, 3/9/60.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "An article appeared in the \"Flint Journal\", Flint, Mich.,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "dated 3/27/60 by Reporter ALLAN R. WILHELM. This article",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "appeared on Page 13. The article reflects an interview with",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "PERRY and in part states that PERRY had received at least 50",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "letters and calls in regard to the photograph he had taken.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "One letter was from National Investigation Committee on Aerial",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "Phenomenon. The article contains the following quote from",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "this letter, \"From past experience with photographic evidence",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "we consider it unlikely that you will ever see your picture",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "again.\" PERRY had advised the newspaper that all he knew was",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "that the picture was in Air Force hands. The FBI only says",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "that it is in \"proper hands\", according to PERRY. The article",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "continued, \"So last week PERRY wrote to the President telling",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "him he can't find out where his slide is and asking assurance",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "that he will get it back.\" PERRY was quoted as saying, \"The",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "only way I will be satisfied if I don't get it back is if the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "Government tells me it is top secret.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
